.description
Very nice interactive display of the the Periodic Table of Elements.
Includes general row and column information, plus a test mode where the
program asks specific questions about the selected element or row/column.
Now is completely AmigaDOS 2.0 conformant.  Path and language information
are configurable from the icon, uses 2.0 proportional fonts, can be opened
on a public screen, and includes German and Swedish name files.  
